On Fri, 11 Aug 2000, Mark Lehrer wrote:
>Could you just recompile these utilities with the 2.4 headers and
>expect them to start working correctly?
As I understand, no.  There's an option to open() to allow large file support
as the application needs to be aware of the possible 32bit int overflow.
